Team repository for the development of the CASi (Context Awareness Simulator)

* Master Branch:*
* The folder "CASi" contains the entire project.

* Docs Branch:*
* A documentation can be found in paper/documentation.pdf.
* Class diagramms for better understanding of the architecture can be found in the "uml" folder.

* Draft Branch:*
* The folder CASiX-Draft contains a first raw idea of the CASi XML Description Language.
* The folder CASi-Draft contains our first raw ideas of the architecture and the entire concept.
